          <div class="card">
            <h3><a href="/en/plumbing/installation/">Plumbing Installation</a></h3>
            <p>Professional plumbing installation. Bathroom, kitchen.</p>
            <a href="/en/plumbing/installation/" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem">→ Request a free quote</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3><a href="/en/plumbing/repair/">Plumbing Repair</a></h3>
